    <superclass name="CM_BaseForm"/>
    <transient/>
    <subclassTransientAllowed/>
    <transientAllowed/>
    <text>Using the CM_TableViewForm
==========================

These are initial notes and will be completed at a later date.

In you local form you will need to reimplement some of the methods.  These are
the methods that are NOT protected. Methods prefixed with a 'z' should not be
overridden.</text>
